# receive.link routing. NO "/*" catch-all: a catch-all rewrite shadows REAL ASSETS (/dist/*.js,
# /style.css were all served as the /app page = 4639b of HTML, so no JS/CSS loaded anywhere and the
# create modal fell back to its stub). Only the explicit, non-file routes are rewritten; real assets
# serve themselves; unknown paths 404. Targets are CLEAN URLs (/app, /home/), never the .html name.
/confirm   /app      200
/d/*       /app      200
/u         /app      200
/          /home/    200
